        "cooked": "<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>I kind of wonder ehhh how do you guys find out stuff from the games? like how do you alter the games? Im studying informatica, but I dont learn stuff like: decipher these old games! rather, Im learning java and php and databases.</p>\n<p>but my second question:<br>\nhow far do you guys know stuff about lba2? for it could be fun to kind of remake lba1 sometime to lba 2 graphics! <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/smiley.png?v=12\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":smiley:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"> or different: remake lba2 in lba1 graphics <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/images/emoji/twemoji/open_mouth.png?v=12\" title=\":open_mouth:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":open_mouth:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>heh, the oppertunities</p>",
