        "created_at": "2007-01-08T20:27:14.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Much of LBA 2 is still to be deciphered.<br>\nList of things to do:<br>\n- Viewing outsides properly, altering them<br>\n- Editing LBA 2 models<br>\n- Editing LBA 2 scenes<br>\n- Editing LBA 2 movies<br>\n- Editing</p>\n<p>LBA 2 has major problems with being modificated. The music and the movies are only stored on the CD.</p>",
