        "created_at": "2007-01-09T17:38:13.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>maybe I will try to make a patch for the lba that makes it just ten times harder to finish the gameif these editors are that good already, could you make there to be a funfrock with a small army?</p>\n<p>Id put him in the last room with two red rabbibunny clones, makes it impossible to live <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"> ok, maybe two grobos thenthose are good too!</p>",
